Support extension for Skymeric RPA
Skymeric RPA is the Robotic Process Automation platform allows to automate mundane repetative tasks.
This plugin is needed in order to automate chrome with Skymeric RPA, the addon does nothing without a running instance of Skymeric RPA running at the same time.
The addon needs very broad permissions in order to record and replay sequences.
This addon does not collect and send any information, you can how ever collect information from webpages using the Skymeric RPA software.
For more info visit out site skymeric.com.
